    <!-- Two column image and text - image left -->
    <section class="bg-dark-green pb-10 lg:pb-20" id="flat-panel-signs">
        <div class="container">
            <div
                class="flex flex-wrap lg:flex-nowrap gap-10 lg:gap-[60px] items-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-full lg:w-1/2 lg:min-h-[632px] rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <img
                        src="{{ theme.uri }}/assets/images/assets/images/signage-and-branding/Career Cabin.jpg"
                        alt="brick wrap"
                        class="object-cover object-center w-full h-full lg:min-h-[632px]"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                    <h2
                        class="font-bold uppercase text-[32px] leading-[35px] lg:leading-[65px] lg:text-[70px] text-white"
                    >
                        FLAT PANEL SIGNS
                    </h2>

                    <h3
                        class="font-medium text-[32px] leading-[35px] pt-8 lg:pt-11 text-light-green"
                    >
                        Budget-friendly and fast turnaround make flat panel
                        signage a popular choice for startups, getting their
                        brand noticed without breaking the bank.
                    </h3>

                    <p class="text-white pt-10">
                        Ditch the bulky signs and embrace a modern look with
                        flat panel signage! This technology utilizes thin,
                        lightweight panels that showcase your brand with
                        vibrant colors and high-resolution images, stopping
                        passersby in their tracks. Flat panels are
                        energy-efficient compared to traditional illuminated
                        signs, saving you money in the long run.<br /><br />
                        They're also lightweight, making installation a
                        breeze and minimizing disruption to your business.
                        The real win for startups? Flat panel signage is the
                        most cost-effective option, perfect for those tight
                        budgets. Plus, the quick turnaround time allows you
                        to get your brand noticed fast.
                    </p>

                    <div class="hidden lg:block pt-10">
                        <a
                            href="{{ site.url }}/contact-us"
                            target="_self"
                            class="solid-button-tall max-w-max"
                        >
                            START YOUR PROJECT
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Two column image and text - image right -->
    <section
        class="bg-gradient-to-b from-dark-green from-0 via-dark-green via-70% to-white to-100% pt-10 pb-10 lg:pb-20"
        id="tray-signs"
    >
        <div class="container">
            <div
                class="flex flex-wrap lg:flex-nowrap gap-10 lg:gap-[60px] items-center"
            >
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                    <h2
                        class="font-bold uppercase text-[32px] leading-[35px] lg:leading-[65px] lg:text-[70px] text-white"
                    >
                        TRAY SIGNS
                    </h2>

                    <h3
                        class="font-medium text-[32px] leading-[35px] pt-8 lg:pt-11 text-light-green"
                    >
                        Make a bold statement with sign trays. Crafted from
                        folded aluminum Dibond, these signs project a sleek,
                        3D profile.
                    </h3>

                    <p class="text-white pt-10">
                        Craving a signage solution that truly stands out?
                        Look no further than sign trays. These innovative
                        signs are crafted from high-quality, folded aluminum
                        Dibond, ensuring a sleek and durable build.<br /><br />
                        Unlike traditional flat signs, sign trays boast a
                        unique 3D profile. Here's the magic: all four edges
                        of the sign are meticulously folded and joined,
                        creating a hidden compartment within the "tray"
                        itself. This clever design allows for all mounting
                        hardware to be concealed, leaving a clean, modern
                        aesthetic that complements any building fascia or
                        entrance. The result? A sign that projects a sense
                        of quality and professionalism, guaranteed to grab
                        attention and make a lasting impression.
                    </p>

                    <div class="hidden lg:block pt-10">
                        <a
                            href="{{ site.url }}/contact-us"
                            target="_self"
